document_data.name: Darts of force
document_data.mainbody: '''Darts of force''' was a [[spell]] that sent [[magic]]al projectiles towards a foe.
document_data.Description: The darts took the form of shafts of azure light that streaked towards an opponent.
document_data.Components: ''Darts of force'' only required [[somatic]] and [[verbal component]]s, with no need for a [[spell focus]].
document_data.History: In the {{YearlinkName|1372}}, [[Pharaun Mizzrym]] often used such a spell. He tried to use it against the [[alhoon]] [[Syrzan]], but it failedâ€”the bolts stopped in the air, fell to the ground, and turned into leech- or tadpole-like things that crawled into a pool. This was because they were actually inside the [[illithid]]'s mind.
